content:
"Raising a Gu to Eat Itself"
On January 3, the Ministry of Foreign Affairs expressed condolences to the victims of the Japanese earthquake, sparking the anger of all netizens.
So far, all the comments below the relevant reports on Douyin have been flooded. Netizens have said:
The Ministry of Foreign Affairs has no power to forgive Japan on behalf of the Chinese people;
This move has disappointed many Chinese people;
If anyone is willing to help, please do so, but don't kidnap 1.4 billion Chinese people;
Strongly support the host of Hainan TV Station, etc.
